    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there is no version of the future where i'm not just... empty. like i've already given everything i have and there's nothing left in the tank. everything is just heavy and dark and i dont see a way to make it better. i just want it to stop. i just want to sleep and not have to deal with any of this ever again.",
