      "content": "i don't know if i even want \"help\" to cope. that's just more work, you know? more talking, more trying to fix something that feels broken beyond repair. it feels like everything is just a cycle of suffering. sometimes i think maybe the only real way to actually find peace is to just... not be here. like, if i could just exit, wouldn't that be more merciful than this?",
